l does this article have%0a716,720c715,720%0a%3c I write this specific article for those people on computer bulletin%0a%3c board systems, and this is aimed SPECIFICALLY at those who refer to%0a%3c themselves as ``computer hackers"   or  ``telephone phreaks". If you do not recognize the value in this article then you are a great fool indeed.%0a%3c %0a%3c Remember folks. Paranoia is our friend. You never know who is watching%0a---%0a> I write this specific article for those people on computer bulletin board%0a> systems, and this is aimed SPECIFICALLY at those who refer to themselves as%0a> "computer hackers"   or  "telephone phreaks".. If you do not recognize the%0a> value in this article then you are a great fool indeed.%0a> %0a> Remember folks.. Paranoia is our friend. You never know who is watching%0a723,725c723%0a%3c %0a%3c ----%0a%3c %0a---%0a>                    ----------------------------------%0a734,735c732,733%0a%3c friends so as to give the eavesdroppers ``misiformation".%0a%3c %0a---%0a> friends so as to give the eavesdroppers "misiformation".%0a> %0a737c735%0a%3c knowledge, etc. If necessary intentionally mislead those friends by%0a---%0a> knowledge, etc.. If necessary intentionally mislead those friends by%0a739c737%0a%3c feed misinformation to an eavesdropper. This can be done to ``spook" your%0a---%0a> feed misinformation to an eavesdropper. This can be done to "spook" your%0a745,746d742%0a%3c %0a%3c (:comment This page has been edited using Pywe:)%0a\ No newline at end of file%0a
